1
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,880
How did we run into a funeral procession?

2
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:13,360
Li Yiran, you can't get away!

3
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,440
Zhuang Qiang

4
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:56,000
Have you come to save me?

5
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:57,840
Yiran

6
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,600
I've come to kill you.

7
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,320
Had another nightmare.

8
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,080
That Linda...

9
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:46,480
She's a total Dragon Lady.

10
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:48,720
Last night,

11
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,520
she made me pull an all-nighter.

12
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:53,800
And this morning she drags me to some team building.

13
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,200
Sicko.

14
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,840
We need the code to get out

15
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,840
Where's the code?

16
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:33,240
Where could it be?

17
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:34,920
Is it here?

18
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,880
These young folks

19
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,320
have no sense of when it's appropriate

20
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,240
Zhuang Qiang

21
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,240
You're so naughty!

22
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,920
I've missed you so much!

23
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,720
You bad boy

24
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,440
I can't wait any longer

25
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,000
What is it?

26
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,800
Don't be so impatient every time

27
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,240
Didn't you say

28
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:28,120
you're gonna break up with Li Yiran?

29
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,360
I'll break up with her the moment I'm back

30
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,920
I haven't wanted to see her for a long time

31
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,800
She's got no figure to speak of

32
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,920
and no money either

33
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:45,120
She can't give you what you want

34
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,640
I really don't know

35
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:48,360
why you're even with her

36
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:50,040
Well, that's only because I was

37
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,800
Too young too naive

38
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,760
and just didn't know any better

39
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:55,680
You're the only one in my heart

40
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,760
Such a smooth talker, you are

41
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,240
Holy shit

42
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,160
Don't stop

43
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,840
Ugh, the stench of love

44
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,480
This is clearly an affair!

45
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,320
Run!

46
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,800
Linda, we should've shaken them off by now, right?

47
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,200
Shaken... yeah, we lost them

48
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,320
Oh my God!

49
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,760
I'm so scared

50
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:46,600
It's okay

51
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,400
I'll protect you

52
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:50,640
I'll protect you

53
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:25,080
You bastard

54
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,760
You've got a mommy complex and never told me

55
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,480
Guess you've never had anything good in life

56
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,200
Boss

57
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:42,160
Boss

58
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:44,560
The show for this team building turned out great

59
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,800
And you performed in it yourself

60
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:47,120
The plot's a real treat to watch

61
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:13,120
May the cheating couple live happily ever after.

62
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:16,560
Didn't you say you'd break up with Li Yiran?

63
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:18,440
I'll break up with her the moment I get back.

64
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,960
I never want to see her again.

65
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:37,280
Yiran, let me explain.

66
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,920
Zhuang Qiang, I'm telling you,

67
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:42,640
what I despise most is a social climber from the country.

68
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,080
If you want to take shortcuts, I won't stop you.

69
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:44,920
But

70
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,440
please don't ever bother me again.

71
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,560
What... what's going on here?

72
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:02,480
That's a lot of pressure.

73
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:14,480
Zhuang Qiang, are you done yet?

74
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:16,160
Is this Li Yiran?

75
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:21,920
Who is this?

76
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:25,120
I'm Director Ma from the Lecang Chunguang Subdistrict Office.

77
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:26,640
Is something the matter?

78
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,640
Well, it's like this.

79
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:29,920
About your mother...

80
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:30,760
She...

81
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:31,640
What happened to her?

82
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,240
Don't be nervous.

83
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,840
It's nothing bad.

84
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:36,000
It's good news.

85
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,280
Your mother

86
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:38,680
in three days

87
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:40,120
is getting out of prison.

88
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:45,840
We just received the notice ourselves.

89
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:48,680
I'm calling just to let you know.

90
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,840
All of you, get the hell out of my way!

91
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,560
What do you think you're doing?!

92
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:07,120
Son of a bitch!

93
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,200
That'll teach you to bully my wife!

94
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:08,800
Pops!

95
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:10,520
Yiran!

96
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:16,720
Son of a bitch!

97
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:13,360
Pops

98
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:17,160
Long is the road to the Yellow Springs, walk slowly.

99
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:21,080
Half awake, half drunk, let your sorrows fade

100
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:26,600
Filial children kneel before the spirit

101
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:31,240
Loose shoes step steady through Yangping Pass

102
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:34,360
Cross the Bridge of Helplessness in peace

103
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:36,560
Ascend to the immortal realm

104
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,240
Return to your rightful place

105
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:42,840
Bless your children and grandchildren with fortune

106
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:49,560
Filial sons, bow your heads

107
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,280
Pops

108
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:21,200
Pops

109
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:24,360
Pops

110
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,840
After Pops passed away

111
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:27,600
I never went to visit Wu Huilian

112
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:29,960
Eight years now

113
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,480
She and I became strangers

114
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:34,960
I don't know how to face her

115
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:37,400
Or how to face

116
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,120
that past that tore my family apart

117
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:42,080
Hello? Hello?

118
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:44,080
Li Yiran, are you listening?

119
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,840
Yes, I'm listening

120
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,160
If you don't come back,

121
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:49,560
then how about

122
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:51,160
you bring her to Shanghai?

123
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:52,880
In a situation like hers

124
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:55,160
she's been locked up for too long

125
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:57,400
Some people just can't adjust

126
00:13:57,400 --> 00:13:58,560
and end up killing themselves

127
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:02,000
or they reoffend and get locked up again

128
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,520
With you by her side

129
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:06,400
we at the office can breathe a little easier

130
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,080
Thank you, Director Ma

131
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,480
I understand

132
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:33,720
Zhuang Qiang sure knows how to put on an act.

133
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,880
Who knew?

134
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:39,000
Putting on a fancy act.

135
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:42,440
He's just a total player.

136
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:47,720
Only good-looking guys

137
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:49,240
get to be called players.

138
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:50,920
Him?

139
00:14:50,920 --> 00:14:53,320
He's more like pond scum.

140
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:57,840
Then don't waste your tears on a scumbag.

141
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:58,960
He's not worth it.

142
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:00,480
You're right.

143
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:02,920
Starting tomorrow,

144
00:15:02,920 --> 00:15:05,240
I'm putting the past completely behind me.

145
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:07,120
I'll find myself a new job.

146
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:09,080
Yiran.

147
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,760
I'm not just saying this,

148
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:13,560
but don't push yourself so hard.

149
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:15,720
Sometimes it's good to take a break.

150
00:15:21,880 --> 00:15:23,320
Xiaofang.

151
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:24,600
What is it?

152
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:29,120
Forget it.

153
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:29,760
It's nothing.

154
00:15:30,400 --> 00:15:31,360
I'm off to send out resumes.

155
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:31,920
I'll hang up now.

156
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:32,960
Hold on.

157
00:15:33,920 --> 00:15:35,520
Like I don't know you.

158
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,200
I know you inside out.

159
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,600
I can read you like a book.

160
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:39,560
Come on, out with it.

161
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,600
Whatever's bothering you, just say it.

162
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:43,000
Give me a good laugh.

163
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:48,600
The subdistrict office called me today.

164
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,360
They said

165
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:55,880
Wu Huilian is getting out of prison.

166
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:57,320
Really?

167
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,600
That's great!

168
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,760
You quit your job anyway,

169
00:16:02,760 --> 00:16:04,200
so why don't you just come back?

170
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:07,000
Think about how long it's been since we last met.

171
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:08,880
Go back?

172
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,960
No way.

173
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:14,200
It took me eight years to move past all this.

174
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,160
Yiran.

175
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,680
The past

176
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:22,320
is best left in the past.

177
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:23,800
All these years,

178
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:25,840
Auntie Huilian's been all alone in prison.

179
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:27,400
It's been really tough on her.

180
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:28,680
Listen to me.

181
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:29,880
That's enough, Chen Xiaofang.

182
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:31,560
Why are you so preachy?

183
00:16:31,560 --> 00:16:32,160
I'm hanging up.

184
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:33,880
Don't!

185
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:36,480
The nerve of her.

186
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:49,000
Go home and wait to hear from us.

187
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,360
Sorry, Miss Li.

188
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:55,600
You're probably not a good fit for the position.

189
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:56,240
Goodbye.

190
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:02,480
Miss Li,

191
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:05,360
why did you leave your last company?

192
00:17:09,280 --> 00:17:10,680
It's because

193
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:13,760
my ex-boyfriend cheated on me with my boss.

194
00:17:19,840 --> 00:17:21,320
So can I take that to mean

195
00:17:21,320 --> 00:17:22,840
you don't handle pressure very well?

196
00:17:22,840 --> 00:17:23,920
They cheated,

197
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:25,480
so why are you the one who quit?

198
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,720
Are you out of your mind?

199
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:29,480
What's so funny?

200
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,600
Sorry, you're not a good fit.

201
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:34,600
Next.

202
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:52,400
Hey, Director Ma

203
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:54,280
Something terrible happened

204
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:56,240
Your mom's been taken to the police station

205
00:17:56,240 --> 00:17:57,840
Hurry up, get back here now

206
00:19:10,080 --> 00:19:11,080
Thief!

207
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:12,800
Who is it?

208
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:17,360
Son of a bitch!

209
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:19,280
What do you think you're doing?

210
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:21,600
Stealing in broad daylight!

211
00:19:22,120 --> 00:19:23,520
And you almost made me

212
00:19:23,520 --> 00:19:24,600
end the family line!

213
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:31,960
I'll kill you!

214
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:35,840
What do you think you're doing?!

215
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:38,880
What do you think you're doing?

216
00:19:39,040 --> 00:19:40,200
Are you trying to kill me?

217
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:41,480
You want to murder me!

218
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:42,040
You...

219
00:19:42,760 --> 00:19:43,840
You're trying to kill someone!

220
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,120
You hag!

221
00:19:50,280 --> 00:19:51,320
See you at the police station!

222
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,280
Officer

223
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,320
I've been wronged

224
00:20:10,320 --> 00:20:11,120
Wu Huilian

225
00:20:11,120 --> 00:20:12,160
Here

226
00:20:12,760 --> 00:20:13,400
Li Ermao

227
00:20:17,040 --> 00:20:18,880
You don't have to stand. Sit down and talk

228
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:21,640
How were you wronged?

229
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:25,400
I'm more used to standing

230
00:20:26,080 --> 00:20:27,080
Here's what happened

231
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:28,840
I was going back to my own home

232
00:20:28,840 --> 00:20:30,120
I couldn't get the door open

233
00:20:30,120 --> 00:20:32,120
Then he shoved that basket over my head

234
00:20:32,800 --> 00:20:33,960
He attacked me first

235
00:20:34,800 --> 00:20:36,000
In broad daylight,

236
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,600
she was hacking at the door with a hammer

237
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:39,480
How was I to know she wasn't a thief?

238
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,120
I was going into my own home

239
00:20:41,120 --> 00:20:42,680
Why do you care how I open my door?

240
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:43,560
I wanted to get in

241
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:44,720
None of your damn business!

242
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:46,560
Let me tell you, Officer

243
00:20:46,560 --> 00:20:48,800
How many times have I told you?

244
00:20:48,800 --> 00:20:50,200
We're in the service industry

245
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:52,120
What's wrong with letting a customer touch a little?

246
00:20:52,120 --> 00:20:52,840
Am I right?

247
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:55,000
So unprofessional

248
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,600
No dinner for you tonight as punishment

249
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:58,320
Wu Huilian

250
00:20:58,560 --> 00:20:59,160
Let me tell you

251
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:00,480
If you don't pay my medical bills today,

252
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:01,880
I'll take you to court

253
00:21:02,080 --> 00:21:03,040
Go ahead, sue me

254
00:21:03,280 --> 00:21:04,960
This was self-defense

255
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:06,360
Why the hell should I pay?

256
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:07,480
Pay up

257
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:08,760
You have to pay

258
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:10,640
The kid's clothes were brand new

259
00:21:11,360 --> 00:21:12,360
Officer

260
00:21:12,560 --> 00:21:14,760
That alpaca peed all over the kid

261
00:21:14,760 --> 00:21:15,920
Look

262
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:17,080
Look at this

263
00:21:17,080 --> 00:21:18,080
If you don't believe me, smell it

264
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:25,160
Officer

265
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,160
That's not pee

266
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:27,680
It's because this kid

267
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:28,920
was hitting our alpaca

268
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:30,280
so it just spat on him, that's all

269
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:33,520
Smell it ten thousand times, it's still pee

270
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:34,760
Your zoo

271
00:21:34,760 --> 00:21:35,800
has to pay

272
00:21:36,200 --> 00:21:37,720
These clothes don't cost much

273
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:39,520
It's a minor dispute. Just pay and be done

274
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,800
No way

275
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:42,720
Officer, look

276
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:43,280
My...

277
00:21:43,280 --> 00:21:45,160
This almost made me end the family line!

278
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:47,560
This is a first-degree disability

279
00:21:47,560 --> 00:21:49,000
Don't be so dramatic

280
00:21:49,240 --> 00:21:50,320
Is this some kind of harassment?

281
00:21:50,320 --> 00:21:51,240
She's a woman

282
00:21:51,240 --> 00:21:52,400
What are you staring at?

283
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:54,160
What is wrong with you?

284
00:21:58,280 --> 00:21:59,880
You're the one who started it

285
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:01,280
You hag!

286
00:22:01,280 --> 00:22:02,520
You're completely unreasonable

287
00:22:02,520 --> 00:22:03,120
You stinking man

288
00:22:03,120 --> 00:22:04,280
You're the unreasonable one

289
00:22:04,520 --> 00:22:05,840
You started it

290
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:06,880
Wu Huilian

291
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,040
Here

292
