311
00:23:22,120 --> 00:23:22,720
Forget it

312
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:24,280
Seventy-eight, just my rotten luck

313
00:23:26,560 --> 00:23:27,360
Alright

314
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:29,080
