318
00:23:34,760 --> 00:23:35,680
Got it?

319
00:23:37,360 --> 00:23:39,160
Come on, you sign one too

320
00:23:48,280 --> 00:23:49,320
Why'd you hit my alpaca?

321
00:23:51,920 --> 00:23:52,760
My suitcase

322
00:24:13,320 --> 00:24:15,960
Come on

323
00:24:16,240 --> 00:24:17,320
Come on, hurry up

324
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:18,680
Officer, sorry about that

325
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:19,680
