326
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:20,880
Here, here

327
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:28,200
Thank you

328
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:43,640
Come on, let's go home.

329
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:26,320
Yiran

330
00:25:26,520 --> 00:25:27,320
Driver

331
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,360
Could you turn on the radio?

332
00:25:29,360 --> 00:25:30,120
Alright

333
00:25:31,760 --> 00:25:32,960
According to our station's report,

334
00:25:33,280 --> 00:25:34,520
this day next month,

335
00:25:34,720 --> 00:25:37,080
