338
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:42,480
The grain begins to ripen,

339
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:44,680
and all the waiting finally bears fruit.

340
00:25:47,560 --> 00:25:49,800
This farce after Wu Huilian's release from prison

341
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:52,560
ended with me losing 800 yuan.

342
00:25:54,600 --> 00:25:57,200
This farce was just like our lives,

343
00:25:58,360 --> 00:25:59,760
with no way to begin,

344
00:26:00,720 --> 00:26:01,840
and no way to fix it.

345
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:06,040
But eight years later,

346
00:26:07,120 --> 00:26:08,280
I still ended up back here,

347
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:10,520
the place I once desperately tried to escape.

348
00:26:38,080 --> 00:26:39,720
When I got home today,

349
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:41,400
the door lock had been changed.

350
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:42,360
That's the only reason I...

351
00:26:42,360 --> 00:26:43,480
You don't need to explain to me.

352
00:26:44,280 --> 00:26:45,880
I wasn't the one who threw the first punch.

353
00:26:46,520 --> 00:26:48,440
What's gotten into you today, Ermao?

354
00:26:50,520 --> 00:26:51,760
That Wu Huilian...

355
00:26:51,760 --> 00:26:54,280
Fresh out of prison and already so hot-tempered.

356
00:26:54,800 --> 00:26:56,880
She nearly made me end the family line!

357
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:59,920
You have no idea what she went in for.

358
00:27:00,280 --> 00:27:01,520
Murder!

359
00:27:04,560 --> 00:27:05,280
I won!

360
00:27:06,800 --> 00:27:08,480
Pay up, pay up, pay up!

361
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:09,760
You're never gonna quit, are you?

362
00:27:12,600 --> 00:27:13,920
Your luck is really terrible.

363
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:32,760
That bastard Zhang Lijuan

364
00:27:33,480 --> 00:27:35,480
Couldn't even bother to come welcome me

365
00:27:36,760 --> 00:27:37,560
Forget it

366
00:27:38,520 --> 00:27:41,880
Every dog has its day

367
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:46,880
You coming or not?

368
00:28:46,480 --> 00:28:50,160
Welcome home, Godmother

369
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:55,120
Sister Lan

370
00:28:56,280 --> 00:28:57,080
Yiran

371
00:28:59,000 --> 00:28:59,960
Auntie Juan

372
00:29:06,840 --> 00:29:07,960
You're finally back

373
00:29:19,560 --> 00:29:21,680
I saw the door was closed just now

374
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:24,360
I thought...

375
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:26,160
