376
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,360
How could that be?

377
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:31,680
I just wanted to surprise you, you know?

378
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,240
Thank you

379
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,560
Sister Yiran

380
00:29:54,560 --> 00:29:55,560
Yangyang, hurry up

381
00:29:56,560 --> 00:29:57,280
Say hi to Godmother.

382
00:29:58,200 --> 00:30:01,200
Welcome home, Godmother

383
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:06,720
Yangyang

384
00:30:09,560 --> 00:30:10,800
Godmother

385
00:30:18,520 --> 00:30:19,680
Yangyang

386
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:21,280
You've grown up so much!

387
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:26,600
Wait a second

388
00:30:27,600 --> 00:30:28,400
Wait

389
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:34,240
Huilian

390
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:37,000
Yiran

391
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:38,000
Uncle Daren

392
00:30:38,000 --> 00:30:39,000
You're all back

393
00:30:47,560 --> 00:30:49,320
Wang's aunt passed away

394
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:50,560
He went over to help

395
00:30:50,760 --> 00:30:51,680
Otherwise

396
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:53,240
For something as big as your return,

397
00:30:53,240 --> 00:30:54,480
