398
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:00,760
Huilian

399
00:31:06,040 --> 00:31:07,080
Step through the door once more

400
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,120
The auspicious hour is here

401
00:31:13,560 --> 00:31:14,760
Fire cleansing

402
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:17,320
Burn away the gloom

403
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:19,480
Let the past drift away like smoke

404
00:31:21,280 --> 00:31:23,960
And welcome a brand new start

405
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:26,080
Go on, step over

406
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:33,960
May everything go smoothly from now on

407
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:35,760
Good luck and good fortune

408
00:31:44,320 --> 00:31:45,120
There we go

409
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:53,960
Come here, Yangyang

410
00:31:53,960 --> 00:31:56,640
Thank you, Sister Yiran

411
00:32:00,200 --> 00:32:01,840
Come on, sit for a while

412
00:32:04,720 --> 00:32:05,760
Have a seat, Sister Lan

413
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:39,320
Last time I saw you, you didn't have this much gray hair.

414
00:32:40,480 --> 00:32:42,760
How'd you get so many gray hairs?

415
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,600
Well, I'm getting old.

416
00:32:44,600 --> 00:32:45,480
Getting on in years, you know.

417
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,960
Bound to go gray.

418
00:32:47,160 --> 00:32:48,040
Not like you.

419
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:49,920
You haven't changed a bit.

420
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:52,760
Me?

421
00:32:52,760 --> 00:32:54,280
I just don't have a care in the world.

422
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:57,320
You, careless?

423
00:32:57,320 --> 00:32:58,520
You're the most caring one there is.

424
00:32:58,800 --> 00:32:59,800
Otherwise,

425
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:01,440
how'd you raise Yangyang so well?

426
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:07,400
Yangyang.

427
00:33:13,560 --> 00:33:15,120
And Yiran turned out just as well, didn't she?

428
00:33:15,520 --> 00:33:17,200
All grown up into a young lady now.

429
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:47,680
Time really flies

430
00:34:00,040 --> 00:34:00,920
Uncle Daren

431
00:34:02,640 --> 00:34:03,560
All these years

432
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:05,920
Thank you

433
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:11,160
You're back now, that's what matters

434
00:34:13,720 --> 00:34:14,880
You're all back, that's what matters

435
00:34:17,360 --> 00:34:18,280
