436
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:21,000
Let's get ready to eat

437
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:24,480
Yangyang

438
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:25,920
Huilian

439
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:27,720
Lijuan

440
00:34:28,640 --> 00:34:29,640
