441
00:34:29,640 --> 00:34:30,680
Come on, Sister Lan

442
00:34:31,120 --> 00:34:31,960
Time to eat

443
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:33,360
Come here, Yangyang

444
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:34,920
Bring that chair over

445
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:41,720
Have a seat, Yangyang

446
00:34:50,720 --> 00:34:51,560
Yangyang

447
00:34:51,560 --> 00:34:52,480
Thank you

448
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:16,320
You're all back

449
00:35:18,760 --> 00:35:19,840
No more crying

450
00:35:20,720 --> 00:35:21,320
Let's eat

451
00:35:26,920 --> 00:35:27,600
Come on, eat

452
00:35:29,200 --> 00:35:30,680
Today's a happy day

453
00:35:31,040 --> 00:35:32,920
We should be happy, right?

454
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:34,680
Right

455
00:35:36,120 --> 00:35:36,840
Here

456
00:35:38,680 --> 00:35:39,400
Take it

457
00:35:42,040 --> 00:35:42,760
Uncle Daren

458
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,680
Yangyang, eat up.

459
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:02,320
Here, Sister Lan.

460
00:36:02,720 --> 00:36:03,440
Eat up.

461
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:06,240
Come on, come on.

462
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:42,920
I'm finally back

463
00:36:43,680 --> 00:36:44,720
Come on

464
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:45,920
Let's have a drink

465
00:36:53,560 --> 00:36:54,440
Hey

466
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:56,120
I've got something to tell you

467
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:12,160
I said I have something to tell you

468
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:13,760
Can't you hear me?

469
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:18,440
It's just the two of us in this room

470
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:20,880
Why are you yelling so loud?

471
00:37:23,040 --> 00:37:25,120
Once I clean up your mess, I'm heading back to Shanghai

472
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,880
Before that

473
00:37:27,240 --> 00:37:28,360
Let's agree on three rules

474
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:30,080
First

475
00:37:30,080 --> 00:37:30,960
Don't cause trouble

476
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:32,760
Second

477
00:37:32,760 --> 00:37:33,960
Don't cause trouble

478
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:36,080
Third

479
00:37:36,080 --> 00:37:37,880
Still, don't cause trouble

480
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:47,320
Did you hear me?

481
00:37:58,400 --> 00:37:59,440
What are you trying to do?!

482
00:38:01,160 --> 00:38:03,400
A little stool trying to climb on the table now?

483
00:38:04,440 --> 00:38:05,760
So disrespectful.

484
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:08,560
You haven't greeted me once since you saw me.

485
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:10,880
Don't you know how to address people?

486
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,280
Yiran

487
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:30,960
You need to pay more attention to how your mom's feeling

488
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:34,120
She'll be very fragile after getting out of prison

489
00:38:34,120 --> 00:38:37,320
Encourage her to keep a positive mindset

490
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:39,240
And reach out to us if you ever need help

491
00:38:57,240 --> 00:38:58,560
A brand new day

492
00:38:58,560 --> 00:38:59,800
A brand new start

493
00:39:00,240 --> 00:39:01,800
Gotta be happy every single day

494
00:39:03,160 --> 00:39:04,200
Right, old Li?

495
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:08,760
Li Yiran, wake up!

496
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:21,240
It's eight already and you're still not up.

497
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:24,000
Get out.

498
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:26,120
Can't a person sleep this early in the morning?

499
00:39:29,160 --> 00:39:31,240
I steamed you some buns and made soy milk.

500
00:39:31,240 --> 00:39:33,560
Don't want it, don't want it! Get out.

501
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:50,760
Get your ass up right now!

502
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:52,040
I'm going to see your Pops today.

503
00:39:52,040 --> 00:39:52,960
You're coming with me.

504
00:39:53,520 --> 00:39:54,840
Ugh, you're so annoying!

505
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:56,200
Who says I'm going with you?

506
00:39:56,200 --> 00:39:57,160
Whatever you say goes, huh?

507
00:39:57,160 --> 00:39:58,560
I just do whatever you tell me?

508
00:39:58,560 --> 00:39:59,120
Get out!

509
00:39:59,120 --> 00:40:00,080
Leave me alone!

510
00:41:03,560 --> 00:41:05,040
In a situation like hers

511
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:07,240
