512
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:09,600
Some people can't adjust,

513
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:10,840
so they kill themselves.

514
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:13,400
Or they slip up and end up back inside.

515
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:14,200
Wu Huilian!

516
00:41:14,840 --> 00:41:16,000
Wu Huilian!

517
00:41:21,920 --> 00:41:22,800
Wu Huilian!

518
00:41:26,680 --> 00:41:27,560
Wu Huilian!

519
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:30,760
She wouldn't really do something drastic, would she?

520
00:41:35,280 --> 00:41:36,600
I'm her mother, damn it!

521
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:37,320
We'll perish together!

522
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:38,360
No!

